{"tid":1434284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［知己知彼］講解一下保皇黨現時既策略","createTime":"2019-08-08T17:24:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T06:53:13.000Z","uid":60120,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e83b82dd760a8bd7cae0209a624bb56cb612f6c7","tid":1434284,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:24:11.000Z","msg":"首先講佢地既目標指數<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">民意</span></span></strong><br />\n可以諗到既背後目的只有兩個：一係保住政策利益，二係欺上暪下<br />\n佢地怕既係反對人數多、選民數量大跌、對政府施政失去控制權、內部分裂<br />\n政策利益一保唔住，阻礙黨派勢力發展，利益分薄就愈易分離，失勢既機會就愈大<br />\n而若果有實際證據顯示反對人數極多，或者會怕埋中央直接問責佢地（低機率bonus弱點）<br />\n<br />\n佢地既主張係<br />\n（１）外部勢力企圖擾亂香港煽動革命<br />\n（２）大部份市民反對暴力<br />\n（３）希望沉默大多數企出黎發聲譴責暴徒<br />\n作用係<br />\n（１）推卸社會混亂責任，爭取時間避免中央問責&mdash;&mdash;同時以外交責任為由卸責中央<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（２）維持道德高地爭取支持&mdash;&mdash;暴力愈升級，支持者愈多，<span style=\"color: orange;\">所以唔會宣佈戒嚴</span><br />\n（３）將支持者眾多呢個訊息傳開&mdash;&mdash;制造成績表以民意團結內部、鞏固勢力<br />\n<br />\n做法係<br />\n（１）定期開記者會，示威者愈有組織愈有物資，更加顯示有強勁外部勢力做指揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（２）愚弄所有人，包括所有愛國勢力、同鄉會、選民、黑社會、警犬、甚至係示威者，營造更多衝突同更多暴力畫面宣傳暴力行為，或者透過假消息自制白色恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（３）定期曬馬，監測民意增減，順便自制成績表呈報上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地怕既係<br />\n（１）冇大台，說服唔到上下既人<br />\n　　　應對：不斷吹風係泛民收美國錢煽動，有ＣＩＡ背後指揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（２）市民克服恐懼並有能力自我維持秩序<br />\n　　　應對：多次吹風各區恐襲、黑衣人四處滋擾市民、吹噓解放軍即將行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（３）一次冇得扺瀨而且聲勢大既全民發聲<br />\n　　　應對：毅進制消滅遊行人數、淡化罷工、淡化反對意見（清理連儂牆、主張示威係由一小部份人煽動）<br />\n<br />\n已動用既資源<br />\n（１）文宣<br />\n（２）錢，愛國和理非、愚暴勢力、非香港人<br />\n（３）黨媒<br />\n佢地依家最缺既係可以幫手做核突野既本地人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要點做自己諗，最緊要對準佢地既主張<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勇武既作用唔一定係挑戰警隊，仲可以係打擊恐怖主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地最怕就係人就繼續出黎，但依然有秩序，冇藉口用更高武力打壓<br />\n封鎖對家使用更高層次既武力將會係成個抗爭既關鍵<br />\n老實講除咗升級暴力搏反cap，我真係諗唔到佢地仲有咩招數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc0335cd1233873d97eacc7482615141d9bf409","tid":1434284,"uid":119485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:28:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4B5XqWt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4B5XqWt.png&h=2edd738f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQGGSEb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQGGSEb.jpg&h=f8cc4264&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dw1Dapa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDw1Dapa.jpg&h=f1f6aa56&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bKDJ5X5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbKDJ5X5.jpg&h=efb6ebbb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UOSKQpb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUOSKQpb.jpg&h=e6dcca84&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cm36bK9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcm36bK9.jpg&h=5ce2c060&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e925a6e1e3ded40de2b695c4f62a06e31225dbbc","tid":1434284,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:31:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5dec366ce96956abd64c9cb6ce190e07e41d18","tid":1434284,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:40:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0f4371fe8ff82783ab58c09b7e3108c2cca7a2","tid":1434284,"uid":21920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:43:22.000Z","msg":"佢d招式用耐左都會冇效果"},{"pid":"6c93c5abe9a9159e42e563394e40d87a2c28891f","tid":1434284,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f0f4371fe8ff82783ab58c09b7e3108c2cca7a2","tid":1434284,"uid":21920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:43:22.000Z","msg":"佢d招式用耐左都會冇效果"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:48:28.000Z","msg":"所以佢最急係要逼武力盡快升級<br />\n難得對方出動黑社會<br />\n勇武更加要打正反黑呢個旗號展示維持香港秩序既決心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淡化攪亂香港呢個污名"},{"pid":"308332b6b065b845b1f9c7c464e4efdb12ec0356","tid":1434284,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:56:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94168b0409a403358754443b4426074103f735b4","tid":1434284,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:03:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d12859fe127d6eabfa3260617f39a53b06fcc1","tid":1434284,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:05:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭者近日大錯：冇俾deadline</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n依家所有證據都顯示<br />\n政府策略係：<br />\n1）所有集會，就算和理非，都刻意搞到極擾民、恐慌<br />\n2）配合記者會，日日抺黑<br />\n3）講明停止抗爭就&lsquo;考慮&rsquo;獨立調查，而抗爭者繼續抗爭，對中間派而言，責任就係抗爭者度<br />\n<br />\n過埋今個星期<br />\n應該俾番deadline<br />\n星期一至五停止抗爭（反正唔會搞）<br />\n星期五冇回覆五大訴求<br />\n抗爭者迫不得已繼續週末上街<br />\n一切責任在政府<br />\n無限loop<br />\n0<br />\n0"},{"pid":"dfa931abc0622ccec304397c73f5b0067ce74be3","tid":1434284,"uid":227699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c93c5abe9a9159e42e563394e40d87a2c28891f","tid":1434284,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f0f4371fe8ff82783ab58c09b7e3108c2cca7a2","tid":1434284,"uid":21920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:43:22.000Z","msg":"佢d招式用耐左都會冇效果"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:48:28.000Z","msg":"所以佢最急係要逼武力盡快升級<br />\n難得對方出動黑社會<br />\n勇武更加要打正反黑呢個旗號展示維持香港秩序既決心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淡化攪亂香港呢個污名"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:08:59.000Z","msg":"但係反黑社會就會變左民眾鬥民眾，兩派打鬥，警察執法拉曬返去。你認真嫁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67a255f93ea089822cead1139c5f05b4ebe7f3ba","tid":1434284,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfa931abc0622ccec304397c73f5b0067ce74be3","tid":1434284,"uid":227699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c93c5abe9a9159e42e563394e40d87a2c28891f","tid":1434284,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f0f4371fe8ff82783ab58c09b7e3108c2cca7a2","tid":1434284,"uid":21920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:43:22.000Z","msg":"佢d招式用耐左都會冇效果"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:48:28.000Z","msg":"所以佢最急係要逼武力盡快升級<br />\n難得對方出動黑社會<br />\n勇武更加要打正反黑呢個旗號展示維持香港秩序既決心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淡化攪亂香港呢個污名"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:08:59.000Z","msg":"但係反黑社會就會變左民眾鬥民眾，兩派打鬥，警察執法拉曬返去。你認真嫁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:01:34.000Z","msg":"法政匯思所講叫be water散水係唔錯<br />\n但實際執行你好難走得切，要前線訊息更加流通<br />\n要練多幾次兵<br />\n<br />\n同埋問題係依家黑主動攻擊<br />\n人地收錢做野，就算你散得到，佢地一樣會散而犬好難即場捉<br />\n如果係咁冇壓力，咁黑咪每次都收錢出黎嚇走你<br />\n仲會愈叫愈多黑出黎，因為佢地唔洗怕受傷同拘捕既成本<br />\n<br />\n除非之後差佬主動打擊，咁就另計"},{"pid":"465cf583e5437b38ca2221b28339afeb28faa0ee","tid":1434284,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfa931abc0622ccec304397c73f5b0067ce74be3","tid":1434284,"uid":227699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c93c5abe9a9159e42e563394e40d87a2c28891f","tid":1434284,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f0f4371fe8ff82783ab58c09b7e310